        <item>
            <title>Audi 设计总监换人　由前 Jaguar Land Rover 设计总监担任</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/massimo-frascella-becomes-new-head-of-design-at-audi/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=massimo-frascella-becomes-new-head-of-design-at-audi</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/massimo-frascella-becomes-new-head-of-design-at-audi/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 14:00:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[audi]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220558</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Audi 的汽车设计一向有不错的声誉，最近他们公布更换设计总监，由前 Jaguar Land Rover 设计总监 Massimo Frascella 接任。<br /><span id="more-1220558"></span></p><p>Audi 宣布，Massimo Frascella 将会在今年 6 月 1 日起接替设计总监一职，而现任的 Marc Lichte 就会在集团内转换岗位。Massimo Frascella 本身在汽车设计界已经有相当丰富的经验，之前曾经在 Stile Bertone、Ford、Kia 以及 Jaguar Land Rover 工作过。</p><p>Massimo Frascella 表示：「简约是我的设计精髓。我热衷于创造没有多余装饰的设计，而不仅仅是追随潮流。相反，我们将会依靠永恒而精致的设计语言。」除了换人之外，高层架构也会有所改变，设计总监将会直接向管理委员会主席报告，可说是更重视设计部门的表现。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.audi-mediacenter.com/en/press-releases/massimo-frascella-becomes-new-head-of-design-at-audi-15862">Audi</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/20/vw-audi-porsche-scout-motors-commit-to-nacs-charging-port/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">VW 集团宣布旗下品牌，北美发售新车将采用 Tesla 充电标准</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/huawei-invite-mercedes-audi-invest-to-new-car-company/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为成立汽车公司，传邀请平治和 Audi 等入股</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/massimo-frascella-becomes-new-head-of-design-at-audi/life-tech/auto/">Audi 设计总监换人　由前 Jaguar Land Rover 设计总监担任</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
